							<a href="http://cocktails.about.com/od/rumreviews/fr/Malibu-Black-Carribean-Rum-With-Coconut-Liqueur-Review.htm" data-component="expertLandingPageRecentArticles" data-source="ArticleSite_Latest" data-type="article.blurb" data-ordinal="12" class="article-blurb">Malibu Black is a richer, stronger, and more flavorful version of the popular coconut rum and it is perfect for mixing into a wide variety of cocktails.</a>
						<div><div class="share-options-container open-right with-msg">
<div class="share-btns share-options popout"
